Loomis Sayles Trust Company, LLC ("LSTC"), a wholly owned subsidiary of Loomis, Sayles & Company, L.P., received a charter to operate as a New Hampshire non-depository trust company from the New Hampshire Office of the Bank Commissioner on February 13, 2007. As of December 31, 2016, LSTC is trustee for and manages more than $18.3 billion in assets.  
 



  







