Collective Investment TrustsLoomis Sayles manages* a broad array of collective investment trusts (CITs) for defined contribution and
other ERISA qualified plans. These private investment vehicles are held in either super-omnibus accounts
or omnibus accounts at the plan level and trade via NSCC.
* The assets are managed by Loomis Sayles Trust Company, LLC, a subsidiary of Loomis Sayles organized under the laws of New
Hampshire.
For more information, please contact the Defined Contribution and Sub-Advisory Management team:


			Brian Hobin
			Vice President
			DC Relationship Manager
			(617) 346-9730



CIT LoginIf you are a CIT Investor who has been qualified by the team, please login below for account
information. For access, please complete this form. Participation in the trust is limited to
qualified investors and certain US tax exempt retirement plans.

Please enter your email address and password.
Name (email address):

Password:








