Fact Sheets








	 			 	
				

   Think Broadly.            Act decisively.         Since 1926, Loomis, Sayles & Company has helped fulfill the investment needs of institutional and mutual fund clients worldwide. The firm’s performance-driven investors integrate deep proprietary research and integrated risk analysis to make informed, judicious decisions.  Using foresight and flexibility, Loomis Sayles looks far and wide for value – across traditional asset classes and alternative investments – to pursue attractive, sustainable returns for clients.          Assets Under Management        GBP billion at 30/6/2017             Mutual Funds £59.1       Institutional £139.1       TOTAL £198.2       DOWNLOAD: Loomis Sayles Corporate Brochure » UK Loomis Sayles Firm Overview » Loomis Sayles History » Who We Are as Investors »   Loomis Sayles at a Glance  FOUNDED 1926  ASSETS*        GBP £198.2 billion at 30/6/2017         EMPLOYEES        659 as of 30/6/2017 VEHICLES        Mutual Funds, Hedge Funds, Institutional Separate Accounts, Collective Trusts         LEADERSHIP Kevin Charleston, Chairman & CEO Daniel J. Fuss, Vice Chairman Jae Park, CIO David Waldman, Deputy CIO         Domestic  Boston Detroit San Francisco    International  London Singapore     Investment Capabilities  Equity   US Large Cap Large Cap Growth All Cap Growth Large Cap Value Focused Value Large Cap Core Dividend Income     Global Global Equity   US Small/Mid Cap Small/Mid Cap Growth Small/Mid Cap Core     US Small Cap Small Cap Growth Small Cap Value  Multi-Asset   Multi-Asset Credit     Multi-Asset Income     Fixed Income   US Broad Market Short Duration Intermediate Duration Core Core Plus Multisector   Global Global Bond Global Credit Global Debt Unconstrained Global High Yield     Emerging Markets (EM) EM Corporate Debt EM Debt Local Currency EM Short Duration Credit   Sector Specific Senior Loans Corporates High Yield Securitized     LDI Strategies Custom LDI Solutions Long Duration Corporate Long Duration Credit Long Duration Gov't Credit    Alternatives  Long/Short Credit     Absolute Return    Long/Short Equity Certain products are not available to all investors and may be offered only to qualified investors.Loomis Sayles's services and products managed by Loomis Sayles are only available in the United Kingdom to professional clients.  This document is communicated in the UK to such persons by Loomis Sayles Investments Limited (LSIL) which is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.  The services and products discussed are provided by Loomis, Sayles & Company, L.P., which is an SEC-registered investment adviser, and its affiliates including LSIL, and may not be covered by UK regulatory protections.Also a signatory to the Principals for Investors in Inclusive Finance (PIIF), a responsible investment framework housed within the PRI initiative for investors focused on expanding access to affordable and responsible financial products and services to those traditionally excluded.  *Includes the assets of both Loomis, Sayles & Co., LP, and Loomis Sayles Trust Company, LLC. Loomis Sayles Trust Company is a wholly owned subsidiary of Loomis, Sayles & Company, L.P. LS | Loomis Sayles and THINK BROADLY. ACT DECISIVELY. are a trademark of Loomis, Sayles & Company, L.P. registered with the US Patent and Trademark Office. 













 

 

 

 






